'''Tamasiḥt''' d [[ajjed]] ideg ttamnen medden belli Yakuc d yiwen, iṣubb ɣer medden s wedmaw n bnadem : [[Ɛisa]]. Imasiḥiyen ttamnen belli Ɛisa ur yesɛi ara baba-s : ilul ala seg yiwen n tmeṭṭut : [[Meriem]] s tezmert n Rebbi. Imasiḥiyen ttamnen bell Ɛisa d lmasîh iwmui ad yeslek Udayen u ad yexelq tamurt n israyil tameqqrant, ɣas akken ur yexdim ara akk tiɣawsiwin-agi, nutni ttamnen bell a d-yuɣal tikkelt nniḍen akken yexdem-itt.  

Deg Tmasiḥt, llan sin n yidlisen : [[inǧil]] d [[turat]], turat idlis n udayen, inğil d timucuha ɣef tudert n Ɛisa.

